hopobject.body: We've got a joint account clindamycin liquid dosage for cats Most of the cash balances the author is identifying are in foreign countries, most likely generated in these foreign countries and the analysis that this cash should be taxed in the US or used to increase US salaries is not that different from standard 19th century colonialism where profits in foreign countries, in a different context, were repatriated to the “home country” ass dividends or wages.
